<h4>How It Works:</h4>
<p>You can list either books you want to buy, or books you have to sell. If selling online, you do not need to bring the book in to the Co-op. If a buyer expresses interest, we will send the seller an automated email with the buyer’s contact details. The seller can then contact the buyer and make an arrangement convenient to both to collect the book and payment. Prices may be negotiated between buyer and seller.</p>
