<p>If you sell your book or dispose of it (e.g. lose it or give it away) within 6 months, it is your responsibility to delete it from the catalogue. We will send a reminder 5 months from the date listed asking you to either delete or extend your listing. The seller and not the Co-op is responsible for any disappointment arising from outdated listings.</p>
